reviewText: Very enjoyable view.Story well acted out.  Singing and music very well performed.Amazon sent DVD when expected and received in unblemished condition.Always enjoy works by David E. Talbert and this was no exception.Look forward to purchasing the next project.
Title: David E. Talbert Presents Love In The Nick Of Tyme

reviewText: I was watching Mo'Nique and she hyped this play so had to see it for myself!  I am not of color but must say I thoroughly enjoyed this play with the twists and turns it took.  Davis Talbert did a fantastic job and had fabulous actors!  I hope he does more plays as I look forward to seeing more rich comedy!Great play!  Buy it, you will NOT be disappointed!
summary: Love in the Nick of Tyme
